    %% COMPONENT: Audit-Test-Fix Loop
    %% PURPOSE: Validate test quality and detect reward hacking through audit cycle
    %% USAGE: Embed after test phases to ensure tests are valid and meaningful
    %% REUSABILITY: Works in any phase requiring test validation
    %%
    %% LOOP_DEFINITION: modules/AgenticGuidance/assets/definitions/agent-loops.yml#loop_types.audit-test-fix-loop
    %% MAX_ITERATIONS: 3
    %% MANDATORY: Yes - must be included after cleanup phases
    %%
    %% PATTERN SUMMARY:
    %% 1. Audit agent reviews test quality
    %% 2. Identifies reward hacking or weak tests
    %% 3. Build agent fixes identified issues
    %% 4. Tests re-run to verify fixes
    %% 5. Loop until audit passes or max iterations
    %%
    %% INPUTS (from embedding phase):
    %% - test_artifacts: Test files to audit
    %% - implementation_artifacts: Code being tested
    %% - audit_criteria: What to check for
    %%
    %% EXIT CONDITIONS:
    %% - Success: Audit passes (tests are valid)
    %% - Escalate: Max iterations reached or unfixable issues

    %% ===== ENTRY =====
    AuditLoopStart((Audit-Test-Fix Loop)) --> SpawnAuditor[Spawn test-audit Agent]

    %% ===== AUDIT PHASE =====
    SpawnAuditor --> PerformAudit[Audit Test Quality
    - Test independence (no shared state leaks)
    - Meaningful assertions (not always-pass)
    - Coverage alignment with implementation
    - Reward hacking detection]

    PerformAudit --> AuditResult{Audit Result?}

    %% ===== SUCCESS PATH =====
    AuditResult -- "Pass: Tests Valid" --> AuditLoopComplete((Loop Complete: Tests Validated))

    %% ===== ISSUES FOUND =====
    AuditResult -- "Issues Found" --> ClassifyIssues[Classify Audit Issues]

    ClassifyIssues --> IssueType{Issue Type?}

    %% ===== REWARD HACKING =====
    IssueType -- "Reward Hacking" --> FlagRewardHacking[Flag Reward Hacking
    - Test passes without exercising code
    - Mocked dependencies returning hardcoded values
    - Assertions that always pass]

    FlagRewardHacking --> CaptureIssues

    %% ===== WEAK TESTS =====
    IssueType -- "Weak Tests" --> FlagWeakTests[Flag Weak Tests
    - Missing edge cases
    - Insufficient assertions
    - No error path coverage]

    FlagWeakTests --> CaptureIssues

    %% ===== COVERAGE GAPS =====
    IssueType -- "Coverage Gaps" --> FlagCoverageGaps[Flag Coverage Gaps
    - Implementation not covered
    - Critical paths untested
    - Integration points missing]

    FlagCoverageGaps --> CaptureIssues

    %% ===== FIX PHASE =====
    CaptureIssues[Capture All Issues] --> CheckIterations{Max Iterations?}

    CheckIterations -- "No: Continue" --> SpawnBuilder[Spawn build Agent for Fixes]

    SpawnBuilder --> ApplyFixes[Apply Test Fixes
    - Strengthen assertions
    - Add missing coverage
    - Remove reward hacking patterns]

    ApplyFixes --> RerunTests[Re-run Tests to Verify]

    RerunTests --> TestsPass{Tests Still Pass?}

    TestsPass -- "Yes" --> SpawnAuditor

    TestsPass -- "No: Broke Tests" --> AnalyzeBreakage[Analyze Test Breakage
    - Was implementation wrong?
    - Were tests over-fitted?]

    AnalyzeBreakage --> SpawnBuilder

    %% ===== ESCALATION =====
    CheckIterations -- "Yes: Limit Reached" --> EscalateAudit((Escalate: Audit Issues Persist))

    %% ===== STYLING =====
    classDef entrypoint fill:#90EE90,stroke:#228B22
    classDef exitpoint fill:#FFB6C1,stroke:#DC143C
    classDef auditnode fill:#FFD700,stroke:#B8860B
    classDef fixnode fill:#87CEEB,stroke:#4169E1

    class AuditLoopStart,AuditLoopComplete entrypoint
    class EscalateAudit exitpoint
    class PerformAudit,ClassifyIssues,FlagRewardHacking,FlagWeakTests,FlagCoverageGaps auditnode
    class SpawnBuilder,ApplyFixes fixnode
